{"tid":385364,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打用過Nikon配件wu-1b?","createTime":"2017-09-03T07:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T07:11:34.000Z","uid":1467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f15ea209151631264e7bbb74be464fb40bb2ec17","tid":385364,"uid":1467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:19:43.000Z","msg":"是咁的，最近接左個係影樓影人像既job。咁個客就要求想即影即睇到相，可以係iphone/ipad 到睇。<br />\n咁我就搵到WU-1B<br />\n<br />\n所以我想問巴打們WU-1B過相落手機會唔會好慢？同埋係唔係我影一張就立刻過落手機到定係要另外download?<br />\n<br />\n如果有其他方法可以無線即時過相推介既話我會十分感謝你！<br />\n<br />\n我用Nikon D600<br />\n<br />\n感謝巴絲們！"},{"pid":"7f56f4091b1a9f8c444d2d544b29d8fa6a21bdc4","tid":385364,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:26:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6eea6f87bac6220cad58163d217f0fb39b0c3222","tid":385364,"uid":123721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:28:47.000Z","msg":"唔係快慢問題<br />\n係根本過唔到如果用ios <br />\n會不段斷線"},{"pid":"516f673f76cc7610be907414c34a16193cae882b","tid":385364,"uid":1467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:32:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真,<br />\n玩wifi用canon啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都見canon好似完善好多，但⋯⋯人窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1837ee768fc5130616e1b0609dfb96787ad4a693","tid":385364,"uid":1467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係快慢問題<br />\n係根本過唔到如果用ios <br />\n會不段斷線</blockquote><br />\n如果用android機依個問題可以解決？"},{"pid":"065ed453e02dbfbf3264ac0a78548e3bcee368a4","tid":385364,"uid":88886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:37:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係快慢問題<br />\n係根本過唔到如果用ios <br />\n會不段斷線</blockquote><br />\n如果用android機依個問題可以解決？</blockquote><br />\n仲哀<br />\n<br />\niPad 過會好ddddd"},{"pid":"4c7d04d74630454c7f22c72e595c92243dc52008","tid":385364,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:41:12.000Z","msg":"間接d都有,但要unplug張卡, 如果用cf仲麻煩。<br />\n1. otg : card reader + usb母頭轉iphone OTG<br />\n2. 即插卡入notebook睇(最方便)<br />\n3. 用線連落lightroom睇<br />\n4. 屌尻個客: 你請得攝影師就好心信下個攝影師啦。(推薦)"},{"pid":"f2d3fc6a5f067a1921b699314d103762dad97968","tid":385364,"uid":1467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:41:38.000Z","msg":"咁如果用wifi sd卡，可唔可以做到影一張立刻自動傳相落電腦or 手機？"},{"pid":"e8b98b33bd15a7a23424790dccc2b528b92d8203","tid":385364,"uid":1467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:45:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>間接d都有,但要unplug張卡, 如果用cf仲麻煩。<br />\n1. otg : card reader + usb母頭轉iphone OTG<br />\n2. 即插卡入notebook睇(最方便)<br />\n3. 用線連落lightroom睇<br />\n4. 屌尻個客: 你請得攝影師就好心信下個攝影師啦。(推薦)</blockquote><br />\n我都想用第4方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但個客懶係想有話事權咁，你知啦，攝影師無人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果用線既我怕唔夠長⋯⋯"},{"pid":"d47706b81d87a1317e94f5b84686ade3309b7ace","tid":385364,"uid":129599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:46:11.000Z","msg":"帶部macbook....直接用USB線啦...<br />\n穩定可靠<br />\n我用nikon D4 配WT-5 幾千蚊 都唔夠穩定<br />\n你個客拎住部Ipad 睇睇下斷線 你又要過黎整?<br />\n而且插入電腦 仲可以即時tune相 設定好個preset"},{"pid":"f4f4c3b9bdfd6b7788b298156e512ba4c1167aab","tid":385364,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:49:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85ef4b48491767c5a7dd8742e7435c4328518cbd","tid":385364,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:36:07.000Z","msg":"我用iPhone<br />\n成日斷線"},{"pid":"db6241e8e1a75a40f2f5db1a79528f2345deb688","tid":385364,"uid":80641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:01:22.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好用 load得好慢個app"},{"pid":"9fbc261dd7928aed90d0b44228b10d4921089634","tid":385364,"uid":88886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re